# create-eleventy-app

This is a starter template for [Eleventy](https://www.11ty.dev/).
You can check out the [Eleventy documentation](https://www.11ty.dev/docs/) or join the [Eleventy community on Discord](https://discord.gg/GBkBy9u) to get help or ask questions.

## Usage

**Start the development server**:

```sh
{{runCmd}} start
```

**Build the site for production**:

```sh
{{runCmd}} build
```

**Clean the output directory**:

```sh
{{runCmd}} clean
```

## Customizing

### Adding a new page

To add a new page, create a new file in the `{{input}}` directory. For example, to create a new page at the URL `/about`, create a file at `{{input}}/about.md`.

### Adding a new layout

To add a new layout, create a new file in the `{{input}}/{{includes}}` directory. For example, to create a new layout for posts, create a file at `{{input}}/{{includes}}/post.njk`.

### Modifying site metadata

To modify the site metadata, edit the `{{input}}/{{data}}/site.json` file. Feel free to add, change, and remove any properties. 
To use a property in a template, use `\{{ site.<property> }}`. For example, to use the site description in a template, use `\{{ site.description }}`.
